          q: "James et al. (2008) found biofilm present in what proportion of chronic wounds?",
          options: ["More than 25%", "More than 50%", "More than 78%", "More than 95%"],
          answer: 2,
          explain: "James et al. (2008) found biofilm present in more than 78% of chronic wounds, making it the norm rather than the exception in non-healing chronic wounds. Biofilm bacteria can be up to 1000 times more antibiotic-resistant than planktonic bacteria."
